22:03.800 --> 22:05.900
Um, uh,
Detective, um...

22:05.900 --> 22:09.000
that, uh, black fellow
with the sweatshirt and sunglasses.

22:08.900 --> 22:11.900
Okay, Donna. Thanks.

22:20.300 --> 22:22.200
We're out here.

22:24.500 --> 22:27.400
- That's your C. I?
