found in the possession of a homicide victim.

25:37.200 --> 25:39.800
- A, uh, Miguel Marquez?
- Was he a client?

25:43.100 --> 25:47.500
- You don't know offhand?
- Offhand? I got a caseload of about 450 people.

25:47.400 --> 25:52.300
Marquez. Marquez.

25:52.100 --> 25:55.900
I got a Marguerite.
No Miguel.

25:55.900 --> 25:59.000
Well, that matches anyway.
We got no arrest record for the guy.

25:59.000 --> 26:03.600
On the back of your card,
it says, uh, March 14, 9:00 a.m."

26:03.500 --> 26:06.300
March 14.

26:11.300 --> 26:16.000
March 14. Yeah.
900 slot. Gabriel Mota.

26:16.000 --> 26:18.500
- He didn't post.
- And?

26:18.500 --> 26:20.100
And I violated him.
It was his fourth no-show.

26:20.100 --> 26:23.000
If you find this guy, let me know.
I'll flag a detainer.

26:23.000 --> 26:26.000
You got an address?

26:25.900 --> 26:28.800
If I can find the file,
