26:43.200 --> 26:46.400
Congratulations. We got a guy here with
background about the crew you're looking at.

26:46.400 --> 26:49.100
Oh, yeah? Is he registered?

26:49.100 --> 26:51.700
No, he's not registered. But
he's robbed your people twice.

26:51.700 --> 26:53.300
We got our own informants.

26:53.300 --> 26:56.300
We don't need to be dragging
everybody in the precinct into this case.

26:56.300 --> 27:00.300
- This guy's got information.
- You mean your guy, huh?

27:00.200 --> 27:02.800
Is it about turf, Ray? You thinkin'
we want a piece of your case?

27:02.700 --> 27:06.300
Anything your guy
can tell me, I already know.

27:06.300 --> 27:09.100
So you going after Ronnie Mo.

27:09.000 --> 27:12.000
- Who?
- Ronnie Mo.

27:12.000 --> 27:16.800
- You mean Ronald Carter?
Yes. He is one of our people.

27:16.600 --> 27:19.300
You put a charge on Ronnie Mo,
you one hell of a police.

27:19.300 --> 27:22.500
- I do my job.
- 'Cause he been dead about six months.

27:22.400 --> 27:25.700
- Got killed up in the Bronx somewheres.
- That's crap!

27:25.700 --> 27:28.900
Look, man. You going after Marvin
Freeland's crew, I'm here to tell you...

27:28.800 --> 27:32.000
Black Larry is the weak link.
He runs Freeland's stash house.

27:31.900 --> 27:34.600
And he's backing up
10-year federal parole.

27:34.500 --> 27:39.900
You put a charge on Larry-
He be steady talking.

27:39.700 --> 27:42.100
We hit Larry's place
this morning. Came up empty.

27:42.100 --> 27:44.600
Every time I hit Larry,
there plenty of dope and 'caine.

27:44.600 --> 27:46.500
Front part of his door
hollowed out.

27:51.400 --> 27:54.300
- Are they still doing repairs on that last address?
- Yeah.

27:54.200 --> 27:58.700
Well, if he is stashed there,
he couldn't have moved it.

28:00.000 --> 28:04.400
We're gonna go back there,
see how good your information is.

28:04.300 --> 28:07.800
- And I'll put it together.
- Better not be wasting my time.

28:07.800 --> 28:09.700
Yeah, you'd hate for that
to happen, huh, Sarge?

28:09.700 --> 28:12.900
- Screw you, Simone.
- Sarge, call for you.

28:14.200 --> 28:16.800
Well, if you're right, Ferdinand,
you're gonna make my week.

28:16.800 --> 28:19.800
