they got that big.44 in their mouth.

28:20.900 --> 28:23.300
- This be it for a while, okay?
- Mm-hmm.

28:23.300 --> 28:25.100
Else you'll be heating me up.

28:25.200 --> 28:27.600
- Take care of yourself on the street.
- Be all right.

28:27.600 --> 28:30.700
Still got some veins up.
Still like my sweets.

