31:49.800 --> 31:52.500
You just gave my C.I.
To that asshole in that room in there.

31:52.500 --> 31:54.700
- What do you need?
- We're from the 27.

31:54.600 --> 31:57.900
Detective Martinez and Medavoy wanted
this guy picked up for an interview.

31:57.800 --> 32:01.100
